        WHEN (sme_lam_kam_1 = '2013' AND lama_kam_1 = 'KAM') THEN 1

1482:
SELECT 
    c.sme_lam_kam_1,
    SUM(t2.valueslist_8) AS total_eur_increase_sme,
    SUM(t3.valueslist_8) AS total_eur_increase_lam,
    SUM(t4.valueslist_8) AS total_eur_increase_kam,
    (SUM(t3.valueslist_8) - SUM(t2.valueslist_8)) / SUM(t2.valueslist_8) * 100 AS percentage_increase_sme,
    (SUM(t4.valueslist_8) - SUM(t1.valueslist_8)) / SUM(t1.valueslist_8) * 100 AS percentage_increase_lam,
    (SUM(t3.valueslist_8) - SUM(t2.valueslist_8)) / SUM(t2.valueslist_8) * 100 AS percentage_increase_kam
FROM 
    transactions_1k t1
JOIN 
    yearmonth ym ON t1.datecolumn_1 = ym.yearmonth_1
JOIN 
    customers c ON ym.ratingvalues_0 = c.numberslist_0
JOIN 
    gasstations gs ON t1.productids_5 = gs.numberscolumn_0
JOIN 
    products p ON gs.valueslist_1 = p sequentialnumbers_0
JOIN 
    yearmonth ym2 ON t1.datecolumn_1 = ym2.yearmonth_1
JOIN 
    customers c2 ON ym2.ratingvalues_0 = c2.numberslist_0
JOIN 
    gasstations gs2 ON t1.productids_5 = gs2.numberscolumn_0
JOIN 
    products p2 ON gs2.valueslist_1 = p2 sequentialnumbers_0
JOIN 
    yearmonth ym3 ON t1.datecolumn_1 = ym3.yearmonth_1
JOIN 
    customers c3 ON ym3.ratingvalues_0 = c3.numberslist_0
JOIN 
    gasstations gs3 ON t1.productids_5 = gs3.numberscolumn_0
JOIN 
    products p3 ON gs3.valueslist_1 = p3 sequentialnumbers_0
WHERE 
    (t1.datecolumn_1 BETWEEN '2012-01-01' AND '2012-12-31') AND 
    t1.productids_5 IN (SELECT productids_5 FROM transactions_1k WHERE datecolumn_1 BETWEEN '2012-01-01' AND '2012-12-31')
GROUP BY 
    c.sme_lam_kam_1, SUM(t2.valueslist_8), SUM(t3.valueslist_8), SUM(t4.valueslist_8)
	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
